dct_title_s: Pacific Coast from Point Arena to Cape Mendocino, California
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, shading and spot heights; depth shown by soundings.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Includes notes and charts on lights, buoys and tides.
